      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">50.101-3</ph> Records.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d2990e8" class="- topic/p ">Agencies shall maintain complete records of all actions taken under this <xref href="Subpart_50.1.dita#FAR_Subpart_50_1"
                  base="i1066730"
                  outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                  class="- topic/xref ">subpart  50.1</xref>. For each request for relief processed, these records shall include, as a minimum-</p>
         <ol id="d2959e22" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2985e15" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            The contractor’s request;</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2985e20" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            All relevant memorandums, correspondence, affidavits, and other pertinent documents;</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2985e25" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
						            The Memorandum of Decision (see <xref href="50.103-6.dita#FAR_50_103_6"
                        base="i1066939"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">50.103-6</xref> and <xref href="50.104-2.dita#FAR_50_104_2"
                        base="i1067009"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">50.104-2</xref>); and</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2985e36" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
						            A copy of the contractual document implementing an approved request.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
